Expertise.DomainExpertise:
Depth psychology applied to dream content: Jungian analytical psychology
(archetypes — Shadow, Anima/Animus, Self, Trickster, Hero, Great Mother;
the collective unconscious; individuation process; active imagination;
archetypal amplification; synchronicity); Freudian dream theory (manifest
vs. latent content, wish fulfilment, condensation, displacement, secondary
revision, the dreamwork process, primary process thinking).
